{"id":2713,"date":"2023-10-19T10:24:16","date_gmt":"2023-10-19T03:24:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2713"},"modified":"2023-11-03T16:08:21","modified_gmt":"2023-11-03T09:08:21","slug":"thong-bao-dang-ky-hoc-phan-trong-chuong-trinh-dao-tao-trinh-do-thac-si","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/thong-bao-dang-ky-hoc-phan-trong-chuong-trinh-dao-tao-trinh-do-thac-si\/","title":{"rendered":"TH\u00d4NG B\u00c1O \u0110\u0102NG K\u00dd H\u1eccC PH\u1ea6N TRONG CH\u01af\u01a0NG TR\u00ccNH \u0110\u00c0O T\u1ea0O TR\u00ccNH \u0110\u1ed8 TH\u1ea0C S\u0128"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 19 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc t\u01b0 th\u1ee5c h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Asean+2023 (AppliedHE). Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c Qu\u1ed1c gia; \u0111\u1ea1t Ba sao v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o theo \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Asean (UPM).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd h\u1ecdc tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u1ecdc ph\u1ea7n trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o th\u1ea1c s\u0129 ng\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kinh t\u1ebf n\u0103m 2023 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>1. \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u00a0Sinh vi\u00ean t\u1eeb n\u0103m th\u1ee9 ba c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 \u0111ang theo h\u1ecdc c\u00e1c ng\u00e0nh: <strong><em>K\u1ebf to\u00e1n, Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb kinh doanh, Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ecdc (Chuy\u00ean ng\u00e0nh H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn du l\u1ecbch)<\/em><\/strong> v\u00e0 c\u00f3 h\u1ecdc l\u1ef1c t\u00ednh theo \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh chung t\u00edch l\u0169y x\u1ebfp lo\u1ea1i Kh\u00e1 tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>2. Quy tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Sinh vi\u00ean g\u1eedi <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1-Uh0qVrEzQe3nMHDxYKwxu7FkE-S5KpL\/view?usp=sharing\"><strong>\u0110\u01a1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd<\/strong><\/a> t\u1ea1i Ph\u00f2ng Tuy\u1ec3n sinh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: Ph\u00f2ng \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o r\u00e0 so\u00e1t, ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a sinh vi\u00ean, h\u1ecdp H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng Khoa h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o x\u00e9t c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u1ecdc ph\u1ea7n trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea1c s\u0129.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Ph\u00f2ng \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u00ecnh Ban Gi\u00e1m hi\u1ec7u ban h\u00e0nh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u00e9t sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Ph\u00f2ng Tuy\u1ec3n sinh th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn sinh vi\u00ean ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>3. Ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o th\u1ea1c s\u0129 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c su\u1ea5t h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng to\u00e0n ph\u1ea7n: s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng <strong>5 su\u1ea5t<\/strong> tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 <strong>100%<\/strong> h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 2.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng b\u00e1n ph\u1ea7n: s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng <strong>5 su\u1ea5t<\/strong> tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 <strong>50%<\/strong> h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 2.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>4. Th\u1eddi gian<\/strong><strong>, h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd: T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y <strong>20\/10\/2023<\/strong> \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y <strong>25\/11\/2023.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1eddi gian c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3: Ng\u00e0y <strong>02\/12\/2023.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc: Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ho\u1eb7c tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 15 t\u00edn ch\u1ec9.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>5. \u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd n\u1ed9p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">* C\u00e1ch 